hanging out,

00:17.167 --> 00:18.301
And i, uh, i have to
respect that.

00:18.367 --> 00:19.700
How'd you like
to stay the night tonight?

00:19.767 --> 00:21.100
Like old times.

00:21.167 --> 00:22.534
That's up to you,
isn't it?

00:22.601 --> 00:23.967
Dan: i'd been given
only days to live.

00:24.034 --> 00:26.334
That was 14 months ago.

00:26.401 --> 00:28.334
