for you.

00:28.401 --> 00:30.501
Nathan's your son.
it could ruin him.

00:30.568 --> 00:32.900
He's doing this
because he wants to bury nathan.

00:32.967 --> 00:34.467
And the deeper
nathan is buried,

00:34.534 --> 00:36.934
The more money he'll have to
pay you to dig himself out.

00:37.000 --> 00:39.100
Okay.

00:39.167 --> 00:40.067
I'm in.

00:47.201 --> 00:49.201
[ woman laughs ]

00:55.833 --> 00:57.000
[ exhales sharply ]

00:57.067 --> 00:58.534
They're excited.

00:58.601 --> 01:01.501
And i didn't even have to
pay them this time.

01:01.568 --> 01:04.200
It's gonna be a big show.

01:07.134 --> 01:10.067
Dan, you reached out to nathan,
and he hung up on you.

01:10.134 --> 01:12.434
He was never gonna
forgive you, anyway.

01:12.501 --> 01:16.700
Sometimes the truth
is all we have.

01:18.334 --> 01:20.634
* information's wrong *

01:20.700 --> 01:23.434
* communication's lost *

01:23.501 --> 01:27.234
* i got to find
what's keeping me up *

01:28.601 --> 01:31.201
* problems on the line *

01:31.267 --> 01:34.167
