before all of this is done *

02:42.733 --> 02:47.700
* don't keep the menace
too long, no *

02:47.767 --> 02:53.201
* no matter what i do,
it all falls apart with you *

02:53.267 --> 02:57.401
* you're such a menace,
and you're no good *

02:57.467 --> 02:58.800
How you doing?

02:58.867 --> 03:01.334
