i'm nervous.

03:10.568 --> 03:12.034
Don't be.

03:12.100 --> 03:14.900
Just speak from your heart,
and don't forget to smile.

03:14.967 --> 03:16.134
You'll be fine.

03:16.201 --> 03:17.900
Mr. scott?

03:17.967 --> 03:19.067
Yeah?

03:19.134 --> 03:21.234
What happened
between you and nathan?

03:21.301 --> 03:23.733
I murdered his uncle...

03:23.800 --> 03:26.034
Among other things.

03:26.100 --> 03:27.301
I'll see you out there.

03:30.967 --> 03:32.934
This should be
the last of it.

03:33.000 --> 03:34.900
I'm so sorry
about all this.

03:34.967 --> 03:36.700
It's fine.
no, it's not fine.

03:36.767 --> 03:38.401
You've been amazing
about everything,

03:38.467 --> 03:39.568
And it just --

03:39.634 --> 03:41.668
I'm sorry.

03:41.733 --> 03:43.334
I'll talk to him.

03:43.401 --> 03:44.967
These aren't mine.

03:45.034 --> 03:47.267
Awesome.

03:47.334 --> 03:48.800
Awesome.

03:48.867 --> 03:50.733
